And you, you're a star above stars, you never hold back. Do you believe in miracles cause I'm sitting next to one right now. You're bringing the old smiles back and Im going to bore myself to death. Before it's all said and done, we will go down in history. And you, you're a star above stars you never hold back. Is life with me as swell as you had hoped? I'll take the fall, and take the bullets for us both. And you, you're a star above stars. 


wee! that song is super =)

*stay with me cause i need you right now let me see your insides* i went out with Lora tonight. we picked up kyle and nick. kyle and nick were mean as shit to me all night long. i drove them around for 50 miles, collectively. neither one had the decency to thank me for the ride. that makes me mad. i felt like a total asshole because i was in a shitty mood and i'm afraid it upset Lora. we went to see the ring. i hate scary movies. this one is absolutely no exception. i sat with my head down and ears plugged for most of it, and for the last 20 minutes, i was crouched in the floor, ears plugged singing to myself. i won't be able to sleep tonight. none of these sentences are very complex. sorry. on the way home all i could think about was shaun... and how i wanted him next to me so i could lean over and kiss his hand, or lay my head on his shoulder. *sigh* i wanted to talk to him really badly, too. i'm trying to convince my mom to change my calling plan on my cell phone. i don't know how well i'm doing. pray for me guys. shaun's my world. (yeah as if you didn't already know) no lies, just love. says: you're a bit special tonight? no lies, just love. says: i thought you were really special all the time sappy crap like that never meant so much as it does tonight... <3

while sitting here listening to lifehouse, i just realized i never thanked lora. i called her up and bawled in her ear for like an hour. and i said the same things over and over and over. i'm sure it was redundant, ridiculous and quite annoying, but being the best friend that she is, she listened and made things a little better. so after i stopped crying, we watched 101 dalmatians together (well kinda.. we watched it together over the phone) and said "awww!" everytime Rolly, the fat one, came on the screen. lora means a lot to me. i hope all of you kids have a friend like her. *sigh*


<marquee>i haven't memorized all of the cute things to say, but i'm working on it. maybe i'll master this art form someday</marquee>

Apologies and i'm sorrys never did much for anyones self esteem. and this is
all on you, its not up to me. I'm casting the lonliest shadow i've ever cast
under the moonlight. you don't gain a thing without putting up a fight. once
the sunrises im sure i won't feel at home. and i never want to spend another
night alone. a second silhouette beside me is all i need. and the loving
personlity staring back at me. i'm sure you'll change your mind at some point
in time. then you can fulfill this beautiful dream of mine.


i don't know who wrote that. i'm thinking maybe jared or something... and he sent that to me way back in the day. anyway, i found it while i was deleting files earlier. i love it. it's wonderful.

i fell asleep about 3 hours ago because i felt dreadful, michelle was gone, and shaun wasn't home. i left my stereo on, playing the songs michelle sent me the other day... all sappy weepy songs except for one. anyway, i dreamt of shaun... and that i walked all the way to canada to be with him, and then he wasn't there for some reason. he called my cell phone and told me he thought we should end everything. at that point, i had been kicked out of the house i was staying at and was walking around in the dark all alone... bawling. *tell me you hate those bright street lights* at that point i woke up, still crying, out of the dark and still alone. i wish i could just hear his voice because even that would make me feel closer to him. 


i was right about lunch, by the way. i have a new resolution; i'm just going to stop eating til i feel absolutley 150% better, and until then i can just be hungry.

quick be silent
don't breathe too loudly
drift into black and white
see the moon shy away
in my world night never turns to day
hide to truth
for it hurts too much


i don't want to make him miserable all the time. it just tears me apart and leaves me with nothing my tattered pieces of my heart. *sigh* i feel awful physically and emotionally. i've never loved someone like that before, but it's all wrong. little hurdles turn into giant obstacles and it's all fucked up. 

i've lost 4 pounds while being sick. mom just took britney, nana and i out to lunch, and it was really good on the way down, but i fear it won't be so good on the way back up. *cries*-- for more reasons than one.




<marquee> angels tears make everything new</marquee> 





i wish i could fix it all and make him happy. i wish i could run away and take him with me. i wish i could kiss his poor tears away. i wish i could be there just to tell him it's okay. sleeping isn't easy without him. living isn't easy without him. why does everything have to be so hard?

i can't help but stare at the message window and pray that he comes back... even though i know he won't... and it's probably better for the both of us that he doesn't. i love him though, no matter what... boyfriend, best friend, or neither. it's pretty safe to say i'm willing to sacrifice almost anything to make him happy. he means that much to me.

shaun makes me a better person.

i spent most of the night with my dear lora. i picked her up and we went out to burger king for dinner and damn was it good. i wish it was less fattening though. but oh well. after dinner we decided to go to best buy cause she wanted to get the nick carter cd. we listened to oh canada the whole way and screamed out the lyrics... and i danced at the stop light, and even got some fun looks from some old ladies in a jeep. go me. +100 points. okay once we were at best buy, i heard this country song that i'm familiar with so i proceeded to dance and sing all around the store like the obnoxious kid with ADHD that i am. it was tons of fun. okay what else... my mom and my sister called me no less than 10 times trying to work out some deal so that britney could get her nails done and i could take her/pick her up blah blah... so that sucked... but put Lora and i at the mall, so naturally what am i gonna do? go by the cologne counter in hechts, of course. yep. so i got high off of allure yet again. it was fun. we got bored really fast... we found a stuffed yak named wak in kb toys. that entertained us for like 3 seconds. some wigger i know yelled out "HEY BRANDY!" in the mall that was embarassing... lora and i decided to start a band for almost every large genre of music.. here are the names SKA: milk in a bag (cause of our new favorite song) HARDCORE: pound (cause L+B=pound and we thought it was funny) RAP: wuddup wigg SCREAMO: morning glory (i think we didn't really decide) EMO: notxyourxstar..... i think that's all i don't know. i sat in the middle of the floor in the mall tonight cause there were no benches to sit in. some really nice old man asked if i was okay, and if i wasn't he would be glad to get me some help. hehe. anyway, we (Lora and i) left, ran by the cologne counter again and sprayed our sweatshirts with allure, and left. OOOH! and i unsnapped my snap-up-the-leg-pants half way up so they looked like wings when we went running through the parking lot. it was really quite humorous. i'm really bored, and i think i'm semi high off my sweatshirt. haha. bye kids.

someone make it stop.

everyone has treated me like shit lately. it's not fair at all. 

i still feel like hell. i'm starving but i don't wanna eat. i had plans but they got cancelled for me... i could go out with someone else, but i'm just contemplating wallowing in self pity for the rest of the night. i really wanna talk to shaun or michelle. no one's home except for me. i feel like a huge loser. bah.

*sigh* i feel more comfortable around him than i ever have anyone else. he makes everything okay.

honeybees get scraped knees today feels like my shoes are untied cause i keep falling down just don't feel like myself today cause you've been gone but only for a couple of days but it feels like weeks in my mind someday in the very near future you should lay on my floor next to me today feels like my shoes are untied cause i keep falling down just don't feel like myself today cause you've been gone but only for a couple of days but it feels like weeks in my mind someday in the very near future come walk with me we'll get scraped knees and these 4am's are too hard too many thoughts running through my head and these 4am's are too hard too many thoughts running through my head today feels like my shoes are untied cause i keep falling down just don't feel like myself today cause you've been gone... yesterday, when i started to feel sick during 7th period, i decided that i had to stay for pit rehearsal or mr seipp would be mad. yeah... huge mistake. i could barely drive home and by the time i got in my driveway i could hardly move. i went upstairs and layed in the fetal position for 3 hours. mom got home and i worked up enough energy to go downstairs and tell her something was wrong and i felt like i was dying. anyway, i was in excruciating pain til 4:45 this morning before i finally passed out from exhaustion. i hate it when you throw up and only feel better for 5 minutes. anyway, last night i only wanted my mom and shaun. i haven't really talked to shaun in close to 3 days. it's driving my absolutely insane. can you go through people withdrawl? i think so. i started to make shaun's cd today. i'm just going to send it to him today or tomorrow. i'm so crazy about him...and i love him so much it scares me. i've never felt like this over anyone else. *empty frames cover up my walls, but they can't hide how much i miss you* anyway, i'm feeling better, but i'm going crazy because i miss shaun. i'm gonna go mail this cd and his stuffed goat. there's no place i'd rather be than in your arms tonight

michelle cheered me up a great deal, which was ultra sweet of her... but i really wish something would possess him to call me at 4 in the morning just so i could say "i love you" and feel completely secure like i always do when he calls. i love him so much. 

*sigh* he is my everything

i can't do anything right to save my life. i'm sorry Shaun.

you know how sometimes, you feel like there's only one way out of things, that's the WRONG way. and if you went out that way people would be totally pissed at your for doing it to yourself? they wouldn't even be sorry, they'd just be mad. well, that's what i'm thinking about right now. it's really not fair at all. if one thing is wrong, it's a million things that are wrong. it's like no one cares that maybe today wasn't the best day, maybe i don't need to hear how my mom's generation was so much better than mine, and that my entire generation needs counseling, and the pain i endured for being fat was indirectly self inflicted, and that, for once in my life i was selfish, and it came back to haunt me. i was awful to Lora earlier today for being sick, and i've just been a bitch to everyone. it's gotten to the point where i'm always mean. mean mean mean to every person there is. i don't even know why. it's like everyone pisses me off in one way or another and i can't seem to get past that. i hate myself.

it's not my fault. =( i can't help it. i'm sorry.
